<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 12. Female genitalia of A-C Macracantha arcuata D-I M. hasselti J-L Thelacantha brevispina. Genitalia are shown in dorsal view (A, D, G, J), ventral view from external (B, E, H, K), and posterior view (C, F, I, L)." , "Figure 9. Females of A, B Macracantha arcuata and C, D M. hasselti showing dorsal view (left) and ventral view (right) A orange morph, specimen from Prachuap Khiri Khan (MUMNH-ARA-MAC 008) B white morph, specimen from Kanchanaburi (MUMNH-ARA-MAC 013 - W 1) C sharp spines morph, specimen from Saraburi (MUMNH-ARA-GAS 018) D long spines morph, specimen from Phetchaburi (MUMNH-ARA-GAS 025)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532445" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/532442" .

